name: Game Technopolis Super Collection 2
overview: This compilation contains: Tesera Kimi wa Kegareta Tenshi ka Seinaru Majo ka!? Hatsukoi Monogatari There's also a bonus section featuring the CD drama "Dennō Tenshi Episode 1: Tenshi daten-shi yattekita!", "Music Room 2" allows you to listen to games music tracks, "Bishōjo overview 2" has profiles of the various female characters from the games, plus a wallpaper collection.
